high_descs: turn left, go to end of counter to the right next to black shelves
go to refrigerator to the right
place lettuce on top shelf of refrigerator, close refrigerator, open refrigerator, pick up lettuce, close refrigerator
go to sink to the left
Turn left and cross the room, then hang right and walk to the counter to the left of the sink
Pick up the lettuce that is sitting on the counter
Turn to the right and head to the black fridge that is ahead of you to the left, then turn left and face the fridge
Open the fridge and place the lettuce inside on the top shelf to the left of the glass then close the fridge. Open the fridge and take out the lettuce then close the fridge
Turn left and then turn right at the sink so that you are standing in front of the sink
Place the lettuce in the sink
anns.task_desc: Place chilled lettuce in a sink

high_descs: Turn left and walk to the white table then turn right and walk to the black table then take a step to your right.
Pick up the head of lettuce that's in front of you.
Turn right and walk to the fridge then turn left to face it.
Chill the lettuce in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Turn left and walk to the sink then turn right to face it.
Put the lettuce in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled head of lettuce in the sink.
